# It appears that I am still not close enough to the iron ore position to place the stone furnace. 
# The player position remains at (0, 0), indicating that the movement command did not successfully bring me to the iron ore location.

# I will check my current position and try moving closer to the iron ore position again, ensuring that I am within the allowable range for placing the furnace.

current_position = get_position()  # Get the current player position
print(f'Current position: {current_position}')  # Check the current position

# Now, I will move to a position that is closer to the iron ore location.
move_to(Position(x=-16, y=25))  # Move to a position closer to the iron ore location
